{
  "text": "A viewing application is also part of the framework [CITATION_1] . It can load large 3D point clouds and the visualization can be customized based on any per point attribute. The visualization allows for experimentally identifying appropriate parameters and thresholds for the classification of a specific dataset.",
  "correct_citation": {
